query:
SELECT t.id, t.codigo, COUNT(f.id) as total_formandos 
FROM turmas t 
JOIN formandos f ON f.turmaId = t.id 
GROUP BY t.id, t.codigo 
HAVING COUNT(f.id) > 0 
ORDER BY COUNT(f.id) DESC 
LIMIT 10;
